getCurrentFieldValues

protected State.ChangeMessage getCurrentFieldValues(State parameters)
Description copied from class: ViewInterpreter
Builds a State.ChangeMessage that contains the current values of all output Fields. Invokes ViewInterpreter.interpret(List, State) to learn some of the output Field values.

Implementation note: Ensure that the ViewInterpreter.interpret(List, State) includes each output Field in its output.

Overrides:
getCurrentFieldValues in class ViewInterpreter
Parameters:
parameters - the query parameters
Returns:
a State.ChangeMessage that contains one Field.ChangeMessage for each output Field
